    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/f3851014f18987727b555dd34dbcb900.avif?t=1768904253\" width=1560 height=821 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在一个被夺去色彩的世界中，一个孩子独自踏上旅途</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个无人能够拥有色彩的村庄里，一个名为「<strong>Fade</strong>」的孩子诞生了——他是唯一能够掌控色彩之力的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上旅途，夺回失落的色彩，并寻求复仇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[灵魂漫游]</strong>是一款像素风格的2D动作类Roguelike游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在横版关卡中前进，闪避敌人无情的攻击，并使用强力武器突破重围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/e1dfc687d3a2bd32f4aad9dc8ef9e60e.webp?t=1768904253\" width=1560 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/67777c827e032c54ae88c78e7c65dbc9.poster.avif?t=1768904253\" width=1170 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/67777c827e032c54ae88c78e7c65dbc9.webm?t=1768904253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>武器切换战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从最初的五种武器类型中选择两种，打造属于你的战斗风格，然后主动切换武器，释放强大的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种武器都拥有能够改变武器形态的强化，使普通攻击与技能转变为完全不同的战斗方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，你可以将灵魂注入武器以强化其属性，在战斗中获得优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/e1dfc687d3a2bd32f4aad9dc8ef9e60e.webp?t=1768904253\" width=1560 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/8a34053a681168760dc6bb07ed27a85b.poster.avif?t=1768904253\" width=1170 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/8a34053a681168760dc6bb07ed27a85b.webm?t=1768904253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>持续的威胁，反复的挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >存在着五个截然不同的区域，每个区域都居住着独特的种族。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寒冷的雪原居住着凶猛的狼族，宁静的森林是鹿族的领地，风暴肆虐的海洋属于鲨族，炽热的沙漠中栖息着蛇族，而魔幻城堡中居住着狐族。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人将不断蜂拥而至，愈发强大的威胁会让你的生存岌岌可危。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迅速击败敌人，收集他们的灵魂，培育战场上的光之树，以获得彩色果实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集这些果实可获得附带强大效果的神器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对超过40种普通敌人、10余种精英敌人以及强大的首领，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个褪色的世界中生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/e1dfc687d3a2bd32f4aad9dc8ef9e60e.webp?t=1768904253\" width=1560 height=46 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/0cb3014d9a434c88df4a36d5af6e864f.poster.avif?t=1768904253\" width=1170 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3224280/extras/0cb3014d9a434c88df4a36d5af6e864f.webm?t=1768904253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>最终审判</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每条道路的尽头，都有一个誓死阻拦你的种族领袖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与普通敌人不同，领袖拥有更致命的攻击和更强大的体力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >检验迄今为止累积的力量，击败领袖，夺取胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
